                            <comment id="13882398" author="stack" created="Sun, 26 Jan 2014 19:34:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Resolving as not a problem any more.  Since 0.96 you can use compress what is passed over RPC by specifying a cellblock codec that does compression.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue probably meant more that this &amp;#8211; i.e. compressing the whole RPC back and forth.  That we&apos;d get if we moved to something like netty.  This is a TODO.  Will resolve though as &apos;not a problem&apos; for moment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
